<p><a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/christopherwalton/2020/04/01/the-domino-effect-5-ways-coronavirus-will-forever-change-retail/#49f4e87866be">The Domino Effect: 5 Ways Coronavirus Will Forever Change Retail</a>. April 1, 2020. Forbes.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/jonbird1/2020/03/29/zero-contact-everything-coronavirus-causes-the-rapid-rise-of-no-touch-retail/#4145250838cf">Zero Contact Everything: Coronavirus Causes the Rapid Rise of “No Touch” Retail</a>. March 29, 2020. Forbes.</p>

